1
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back in Graycastle,</i></font>

2
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fourth Prince Roland Wimbledon 
was already notorious.</i></font>

3
00:00:35,260 --> 00:00:37,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A life of debauchery, utter incompetence,</i></font>

4
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:41,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>not a shred of noble grace... 
the list goes on.</i></font>

5
00:00:41,290 --> 00:00:45,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Compared to his four siblings, 
he was worlds apart.</i></font>

6
00:00:45,950 --> 00:00:51,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ah, why was I sent to assist 
him in the Royal Decree?</i></font>

7
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:53,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If His Majesty hadn't promised 
to appoint me as the</i></font>

8
00:00:53,990 --> 00:00:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>official Finance Minister once 
the Royal Decree concluded,</i></font>

9
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wouldn't have come to 
this godforsaken place.</i></font>

10
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:02,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And yet, things began to change.</i></font>

11
00:01:02,700 --> 00:01:05,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When exactly did it start?</i></font>

12
00:01:06,370 --> 00:01:11,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Probably around the time 
he saved that witch.</i></font>

13
00:01:11,220 --> 00:01:15,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His Highness Roland displayed a 
sharp mind and grand strategic vision.</i></font>

14
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:17,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He skillfully avoided his own predicament,</i></font>

15
00:01:17,990 --> 00:01:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and struck at the very 
essence of theocracy.</i></font>

16
00:01:20,710 --> 00:01:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>By using witches, he set his sights 
directly on the Church of Hermes.</i></font>

17
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At first, I thought it was 
just baseless rhetoric.</i></font>

18
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then, His Highness spent all night 
studying financial reports,</i></font>

19
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>formulating trade strategies,</i></font>

20
00:01:34,130 --> 00:01:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and even proposed something 
called the "Silk Road."</i></font>

21
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:40,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Heaven knows where he learned those words.</i></font>

22
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, to possess such a long-term vision,</i></font>

23
00:01:43,230 --> 00:01:47,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>while keeping his focus squarely on the 
immediate development of Border Town,</i></font>

24
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:50,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>this is no baseless fantasy.</i></font>

25
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if we cannot survive 
the Months of Demons,</i></font>

26
00:01:53,850 --> 00:01:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>everything will be for nothing.</i></font>

27
00:01:56,820 --> 00:02:01,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hear from Carter that His Highness 
now plans to build a city wall.</i></font>

28
00:02:01,730 --> 00:02:04,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Winter is just over three months away.</i></font>

29
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:08,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if it's only around 2000 feet long, 
it should be theoretically impossible.</i></font>

30
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But His Highness has already 
surprised me so many times.</i></font>

31
00:02:12,230 --> 00:02:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's still three months left.</i></font>

32
00:02:13,570 --> 00:02:17,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If it really can't be done, 
there's still time to run away.</i></font>

33
00:02:17,730 --> 00:02:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How will His Highness build a 
city wall in just three months?</i></font>

34
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>From here on, things are only 
getting more interesting.</i></font>

35
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful. Move it over there.</font>

36
00:04:48,330 --> 00:04:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go to the North Mountain mine and 
bring back a cartload of limestone.</font>

37
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also get a cartload of clay, 
something like this.</font>

38
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then have someone crush them into 
small pieces, mix them thoroughly,</font>

39
00:04:58,030 --> 00:05:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and spread the mixture evenly 
in the pit in the firing room.</font>

40
00:05:07,450 --> 00:05:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave the rest to Miss Anna.</font>

41
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carter, get someone to 
crush this clinker.</font>

42
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mix it with gypsum at a 10:1 
ratio and grind it into powder.</font>

43
00:05:46,790 --> 00:05:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, what is this for?</font>

44
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A new formula from the alchemy workshop.</font>

45
00:05:54,590 --> 00:05:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, everything is 
prepared as you instructed.</font>

46
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly are you making?</font>

47
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Anna, this time, 
let me show you a bit of magic.</font>

48
00:06:09,530 --> 00:06:11,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, you can use magic too?</font>

49
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:16,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. A kind of magic called science.</font>

50
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Science?</font>

51
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carter, mix this powder with water 
and pour it onto those stones over there.</font>

52
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pour it into the gaps, so that it's 
evenly spread between the stones.</font>

53
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By tomorrow, they will 
become a solid wall.</font>

54
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:31,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? You must be joking!</font>

55
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Anna, do you believe me?</font>

56
00:06:34,670 --> 00:06:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever you say, I believe you.</font>

57
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then do as I say.</font>

58
00:06:39,470 --> 00:06:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's wait and see.</font>

59
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:44,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, Your Highness.</font>

60
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on, Carter.</font>

61
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Test its strength.</font>

62
00:07:15,490 --> 00:07:17,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">T-This is truly incredible, Your Highness.</font>

63
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:21,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With this, we can build our 
city wall as fast as we want.</font>

64
00:07:21,180 --> 00:07:24,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A border wall in five years 
would be well within reach.</font>

65
00:07:24,140 --> 00:07:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We could even use it to 
reinforce this castle,</font>

66
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">making it the strongest, 
safest castle in Graycastle.</font>

67
00:07:29,340 --> 00:07:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not just the castle.</font>

68
00:07:30,580 --> 00:07:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll use it to build much more.</font>

69
00:07:32,990 --> 00:07:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Much more?</font>

70
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:42,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could I have ten thousand mansions,</i></font>

71
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>sheltering all the poor scholars 
and making them rejoice.</i></font>

72
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, what did you say?</font>

73
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll use it to build a 
better home for everyone.</font>

74
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:57,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone can live in a sturdy house,</font>

75
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">one that neither storms 
nor blizzards can destroy.</font>

76
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Anna, starting today,</font>

77
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">please fire a batch every day.</font>

78
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:08,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

79
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carter, you're in charge 
of wall construction.</font>

80
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:14,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure it's built within three months.</font>

81
00:08:14,110 --> 00:08:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

82
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:16,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave it to me.</font>

83
00:08:22,290 --> 00:08:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, by the way, Your Highness,</font>

84
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:27,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what is this miraculous 
alchemical powder called?</font>

85
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cement.</font>

86
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What... What is this?</i></font>

87
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

88
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:51,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So many days have passed.</font>

89
00:08:51,110 --> 00:08:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is construction moving so slowly?</font>

90
00:08:53,050 --> 00:08:54,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's crooked and uneven.</font>

91
00:08:54,890 --> 00:08:56,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't even stand on it properly.</font>

92
00:08:56,450 --> 00:08:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget holding off demonic beasts,</font>

93
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it'd collapse in the first rain.</font>

94
00:08:59,140 --> 00:09:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apologies, Your Highness.</font>

95
00:09:00,390 --> 00:09:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is my responsibility.</font>

96
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, if I may speak frankly,</font>

97
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carter has no prior 
experience in such matters.</font>

98
00:09:08,090 --> 00:09:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For a wall over 2000 feet long,</font>

99
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:13,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without an experienced architect 
to oversee the work,</font>

100
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:18,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even with this miraculous 
alchemical agent called "cement,"</font>

101
00:09:18,860 --> 00:09:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it would be difficult to meet 
Your Highness's expectations.</font>

102
00:09:22,090 --> 00:09:25,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need a true master stonemason.</font>

103
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A master stonemason...</font>

104
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:31,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go and recruit one immediately, 
no matter the cost.</font>

105
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Your Highness, 
it's not a matter of money.</font>

106
00:09:34,420 --> 00:09:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no one with this kind 
of expertise in Border Town.</font>

107
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:41,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then look for one in 
Longsong Stronghold or Willow Town.</font>

108
00:09:41,410 --> 00:09:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you have to go back 
to Graycastle, find someone.</font>

109
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Professor Karl!</font>

110
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:31,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

111
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've become...</font>

112
00:10:35,420 --> 00:10:37,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've become a witch too.</font>

113
00:10:40,860 --> 00:10:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. van Bate, could you 
please come over here?</font>

114
00:10:48,570 --> 00:10:49,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's happened?</font>

115
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please take a look at this notice for us.</font>

116
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say the prince posted it.</font>

117
00:10:53,470 --> 00:10:55,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does it say?</font>

118
00:10:55,350 --> 00:10:57,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By decree of Roland Wimbledon,</font>

119
00:10:57,130 --> 00:10:59,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fourth Prince of
the Kingdom of Graycastle:</font>

120
00:10:59,100 --> 00:11:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Urgent recruitment for 
the following positions:</font>

121
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stonebreakers: male, 
ages 20 - 40, physically strong.</font>

122
00:11:06,390 --> 00:11:08,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daily wage: 25 bronze royals.</font>

123
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Masons: Any gender, 
ages 18+, with masonry experience.</font>

124
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:14,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daily wage: 45 bronze royals.</font>

125
00:11:14,780 --> 00:11:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Laborers: male, ages 18+.</font>

126
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:19,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daily wage: 12 bronze royals.</font>

127
00:11:19,870 --> 00:11:22,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master stonemasons: Any gender, any age.</font>

128
00:11:22,990 --> 00:11:24,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must have experience in 
municipal construction,</font>

129
00:11:24,940 --> 00:11:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">fortress building, 
or large-scale engineering projects.</font>

130
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Monthly wage: 1 gold royal.</font>

131
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those with exceptional 
experience and performance</font>

132
00:11:31,430 --> 00:11:32,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">may be granted official positions.</font>

133
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fourth Prince of the 
Kingdom of Graycastle, Roland Wimbledon.</font>

134
00:11:36,350 --> 00:11:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I hear that right?</font>

135
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could even become an official,</font>

136
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:41,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">maybe see His Highness 
the Prince every day!</font>

137
00:11:42,330 --> 00:11:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. van Bate, Mr. van Bate!</font>

138
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A master stonemason came 
to apply so quickly?</font>

139
00:11:49,830 --> 00:11:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you say finding one would be hard?</font>

140
00:11:51,850 --> 00:11:53,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm surprised too.</font>

141
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:55,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The man is clearly a local teacher,</font>

142
00:11:55,820 --> 00:11:59,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yet he claims to have experience 
in large-scale construction projects.</font>

143
00:11:59,530 --> 00:12:01,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, would you like to see him?</font>

144
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:05,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. Bring him in.</font>

145
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're here to apply 
as master stonemason?</font>

146
00:12:07,850 --> 00:12:09,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

147
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Karl van Bate.</font>

148
00:12:11,900 --> 00:12:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard you used to teach in town.</font>

149
00:12:14,850 --> 00:12:17,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just taught the children to recognize 
their names, Your Highness.</font>

150
00:12:17,980 --> 00:12:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then what qualifies you for this position?</font>

151
00:12:19,890 --> 00:12:24,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... have participated in the maintenance 
of embankments within Graycastle,</font>

152
00:12:24,690 --> 00:12:26,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the design and construction of the palace,</font>

153
00:12:26,350 --> 00:12:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the renovation of 
various public facilities.</font>

154
00:12:30,580 --> 00:12:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean you've been involved in many 
major construction projects in Graycastle?</font>

155
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

156
00:12:37,430 --> 00:12:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All large-scale construction in Graycastle</font>

157
00:12:39,970 --> 00:12:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is handled by the Mason Guild.</font>

158
00:12:42,260 --> 00:12:45,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you a member of the 
Graycastle Mason Guild?</font>

159
00:12:46,410 --> 00:12:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

160
00:12:49,010 --> 00:12:51,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Mason Guild's members 
are naturally elites.</font>

161
00:12:51,020 --> 00:12:54,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But as I recall, during construction of 
the Graycastle Theater a few years ago,</font>

162
00:12:54,110 --> 00:12:55,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a collapse occurred.</font>

163
00:12:55,970 --> 00:12:57,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The entire Mason Guild was convicted</font>

164
00:12:57,930 --> 00:12:59,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and executed.</font>

165
00:13:01,460 --> 00:13:04,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is indeed how the 
story spread outside.</font>

166
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:06,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Then what really happened?</font>

167
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The administrator at the time,</font>

168
00:13:09,150 --> 00:13:11,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for a kickback of several 
hundred gold royals,</font>

169
00:13:11,260 --> 00:13:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">ordered us to switch the stone,</font>

170
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which led to the accident.</font>

171
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:17,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We warned the administrator 
many times that</font>

172
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">using that grade of stone would 
compromise structural integrity.</font>

173
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But no one listened.</font>

174
00:13:23,650 --> 00:13:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After the accident,</font>

175
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we explained everything 
to the investigators.</font>

176
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the official who 
ordered the substitution</font>

177
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">claimed that it was to save costs.</font>

178
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:37,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, he was deemed to have 
good intentions and was acquitted.</font>

179
00:13:37,970 --> 00:13:41,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The entire Mason Guild 
was sentenced to death.</font>

180
00:13:42,350 --> 00:13:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard rumors beforehand 
and fled overnight.</font>

181
00:13:45,350 --> 00:13:48,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to Border Town 
and have hidden my identity ever since.</font>

182
00:13:48,830 --> 00:13:50,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you've been hiding your identity,</font>

183
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why are you revealing yourself 
and applying for the job now?</font>

184
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:57,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because...  I have a reason 
I can no longer stay silent.</font>

185
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What reason?</font>

186
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

187
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Your Highness.</font>

188
00:14:02,850 --> 00:14:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot yet reveal my reason.</font>

189
00:14:05,610 --> 00:14:06,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness,</font>

190
00:14:07,910 --> 00:14:10,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you have doubts about me.</font>

191
00:14:10,460 --> 00:14:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, I defied the investigation 
and fled, a capital offense.</font>

192
00:14:13,860 --> 00:14:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I really had no choice.</font>

193
00:14:15,690 --> 00:14:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I hadn't fled, 
I wouldn't be alive today.</font>

194
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:20,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been a stonemason my whole life.</font>

195
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can definitely meet your requirements.</font>

196
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please give me a chance 
to atone for my sins.</font>

197
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov, what do you think?</font>

198
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:35,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, I believe this 
man is mostly telling the truth.</font>

199
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By law, he is now a fugitive 
guilty of a crime.</font>

200
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, considering your 
current needs, Your Highness,</font>

201
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it would be wise 
to make an exception.</font>

202
00:14:50,780 --> 00:14:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. van Bate, I pardon your crimes 
and appoint you as Master Stonemason.</font>

203
00:14:54,180 --> 00:14:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From now on, you're a member 
of the administrative office.</font>

204
00:14:57,320 --> 00:15:00,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show me what a master 
from the Mason Guild can do.</font>

205
00:15:03,830 --> 00:15:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to build a city wall here,</font>

206
00:15:05,740 --> 00:15:07,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">from the Dragonspine Mountain 
to the Redwater River,</font>

207
00:15:07,870 --> 00:15:09,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">roughly 2000 feet in length.</font>

208
00:15:10,550 --> 00:15:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fifteen feet high, six feet wide,</font>

209
00:15:12,300 --> 00:15:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wide enough for four men to walk abreast.</font>

210
00:15:14,450 --> 00:15:16,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? How would you go about it?</font>

211
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:20,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, to stabilize the upper structure,</font>

212
00:15:20,090 --> 00:15:22,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll need to dig a trench one man deep.</font>

213
00:15:22,010 --> 00:15:26,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if the top is six feet wide 
and the wall is 15 feet high,</font>

214
00:15:26,710 --> 00:15:29,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then the base must be at 
least twice that width.</font>

215
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Your Highness provides me with 150 men,</font>

216
00:15:31,740 --> 00:15:33,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can complete the trench in three months.</font>

217
00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:37,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The upper wall must be 
built with solid stone.</font>

218
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:39,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cutting and polishing the 
stone will take a lot of time.</font>

219
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:42,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The whole project will probably 
take three years to complete.</font>

220
00:15:46,470 --> 00:15:48,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A ditch won't stop the demonic beasts.</font>

221
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop the demonic beasts...</font>

222
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:51,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You... You mean...</font>

223
00:15:52,470 --> 00:15:56,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I need to build a wall 
capable of holding back demonic beasts.</font>

224
00:15:56,490 --> 00:15:59,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Therefore, it must be completed before 
the Months of Demons arrive this year.</font>

225
00:15:59,780 --> 00:16:00,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can it be done?</font>

226
00:16:01,610 --> 00:16:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if that's the case...</font>

227
00:16:05,610 --> 00:16:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then the wall doesn't need 
to be built that high.</font>

228
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like this...</font>

229
00:16:10,580 --> 00:16:12,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the height is reduced to 12 feet,</font>

230
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the width reduced by a third,</font>

231
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then the base width shrinks to 6 feet.</font>

232
00:16:18,300 --> 00:16:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can dig the trench and 
build the wall simultaneously.</font>

233
00:16:20,830 --> 00:16:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we increase the workforce to 200,</font>

234
00:16:24,020 --> 00:16:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the foundation could be dug 
in about a month and a half.</font>

235
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

236
00:16:30,090 --> 00:16:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what?</font>

237
00:16:32,010 --> 00:16:35,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Building the wall requires 
a lot of cut stone.</font>

238
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In such a short time,</font>

239
00:16:36,880 --> 00:16:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there's no way we can 
process enough stone.</font>

240
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if we bought it from nearby towns,</font>

241
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">factoring in transport time,</font>

242
00:16:43,560 --> 00:16:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm afraid it's still...</font>

243
00:16:45,540 --> 00:16:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So if we had enough stone,</font>

244
00:16:47,540 --> 00:16:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you could build the wall 
within three months?</font>

245
00:16:49,820 --> 00:16:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe so, yes.</font>

246
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

247
00:16:52,380 --> 00:16:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you don't need to worry.</font>

248
00:16:54,370 --> 00:16:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come with me. 
I'll show you something.</font>

249
00:16:57,520 --> 00:16:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay.</font>

250
00:17:04,290 --> 00:17:06,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is amazing.</font>

251
00:17:06,450 --> 00:17:07,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's incredible!</font>

252
00:17:08,770 --> 00:17:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They... They've bonded so solidly.</font>

253
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:16,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With this, it's like having stone 
blocks in any shape we need,</font>

254
00:17:16,620 --> 00:17:18,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without cutting or polishing.</font>

255
00:17:22,170 --> 00:17:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we can eliminate the 
time-consuming step of processing stone,</font>

256
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:27,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the speed of any construction project</font>

257
00:17:27,390 --> 00:17:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will reach an entirely new level.</font>

258
00:17:28,900 --> 00:17:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? With this, can you 
finish in three months?</font>

259
00:17:31,890 --> 00:17:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. This substance is magnificent.</font>

260
00:17:34,540 --> 00:17:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, what did 
you say it was called?</font>

261
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cement.</font>

262
00:17:37,800 --> 00:17:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cement. I'll remember that.</font>

263
00:17:39,970 --> 00:17:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe the alchemy workshop 
developed something this amazing.</font>

264
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:48,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll write you some detailed 
instructions on how to use cement.</font>

265
00:17:48,190 --> 00:17:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you need anything else, 
speak with my assistant minister, Barov.</font>

266
00:17:51,990 --> 00:17:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

267
00:17:54,930 --> 00:17:58,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, actually, 
there's one more thing.</font>

268
00:17:58,480 --> 00:17:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? What is it?</font>

269
00:17:59,990 --> 00:18:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's...</font>

270
00:18:04,940 --> 00:18:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anna!</font>

271
00:18:08,570 --> 00:18:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Professor Karl!</font>

272
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:18,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, he's the aforementioned Professor Karl.</font>

273
00:18:18,840 --> 00:18:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, many of the town's children 
go to his house for lessons.</font>

274
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:24,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's really kind to us.</font>

275
00:18:25,430 --> 00:18:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only told them stories 
and taught them a few words.</font>

276
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:32,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anna, I thought you were dead.</font>

277
00:18:32,530 --> 00:18:35,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been having nightmares 
these past few days.</font>

278
00:18:35,610 --> 00:18:38,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's such a relief you're alive.</font>

279
00:18:39,410 --> 00:18:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

280
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, thank you for your mercy.</font>

281
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be like that. Please get up.</font>

282
00:18:47,100 --> 00:18:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness...</font>

283
00:18:48,100 --> 00:18:51,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. van Bate, to me,</font>

284
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">witches aren't the 
embodiment of the Devil.</font>

285
00:18:53,460 --> 00:18:56,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I certainly won't hunt them 
down as the Church commands.</font>

286
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Anna is innocent.</font>

287
00:18:58,260 --> 00:18:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I'd never harm her.</font>

288
00:18:59,790 --> 00:19:02,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, 
there's something I must tell you.</font>

289
00:19:06,190 --> 00:19:08,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, what is it?</font>

290
00:19:08,060 --> 00:19:10,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember I mentioned earlier</font>

291
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:13,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that I had my own reason 
for coming to apply?</font>

292
00:19:13,550 --> 00:19:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't dare tell you then,</font>

293
00:19:15,330 --> 00:19:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but now, I'm certain I can.</font>

294
00:19:19,040 --> 00:19:23,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In this Border Town, 
there is another witch.</font>

295
00:19:36,250 --> 00:19:37,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can this be?</font>

296
00:19:38,270 --> 00:19:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even Nana... has become a witch too?</font>

297
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would've thought that 
in this tiny Border Town,</font>

298
00:19:45,650 --> 00:19:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there would be two witches?</font>

299
00:19:47,130 --> 00:19:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If this were anywhere else,</i></font>

300
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>there would be another bloody witch hunt.</i></font>

301
00:19:52,020 --> 00:19:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But how will His Highness react here?</i></font>

302
00:20:02,700 --> 00:20:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is what I wish to ask 
of you, Your Highness.</font>

303
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:08,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness is merciful and 
unafraid of the rumors of the Devil.</font>

304
00:20:08,420 --> 00:20:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Anna's good fortune 
to be able to join your harem.</font>

305
00:20:12,760 --> 00:20:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although Nana is still 
young and cannot serve you,</font>

306
00:20:16,540 --> 00:20:18,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she is truly innocent.</font>

307
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:20,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I beg you, Your Highness,</font>

308
00:20:20,310 --> 00:20:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">please save her too.</font>

309
00:20:23,170 --> 00:20:24,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not what you think.</font>

310
00:20:24,610 --> 00:20:27,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saved Anna because I need her help.</font>

311
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I believe that once Nana grows up,</font>

312
00:20:29,840 --> 00:20:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she'll definitely be able to help you too.</font>

313
00:20:34,670 --> 00:20:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You truly misunderstand.</font>

314
00:20:36,540 --> 00:20:41,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Anna's job is to make 
the cement I just showed you.</font>

315
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:42,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

316
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:46,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That miraculous substance 
was actually made by Anna?</font>

317
00:20:46,860 --> 00:20:48,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As for this Nana you mentioned,</font>

318
00:20:48,410 --> 00:20:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to meet her.</font>

319
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:51,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can guarantee her safety.</font>

320
00:20:51,700 --> 00:20:53,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you bring her to me?</font>

321
00:20:53,030 --> 00:20:55,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! Yes, Your Highness.</font>

322
00:20:55,030 --> 00:20:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand.</font>

323
00:20:56,180 --> 00:20:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forgive me, Your Highness.</font>

324
00:20:57,860 --> 00:21:00,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I am truly grateful to you.</font>

325
00:21:02,140 --> 00:21:05,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go. We'll discuss 
details back in my chambers.</font>

326
00:21:06,060 --> 00:21:07,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

327
00:21:08,010 --> 00:21:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Anna, I'll leave matters here to you.</font>

328
00:21:10,730 --> 00:21:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

329
00:21:15,780 --> 00:21:17,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness. Your Highness!</font>

330
00:21:17,660 --> 00:21:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Barov?</font>

331
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:22,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, I understand 
your eagerness to meet this witch.</font>

332
00:21:22,350 --> 00:21:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, there might be a complication.</font>

333
00:21:25,610 --> 00:21:27,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? What is it?</font>

334
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, this girl's name 
is Nana Pine, right?</font>

335
00:21:31,890 --> 00:21:34,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The surname Pine doesn't 
belong to commoners.</font>

336
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:38,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It belongs to a minor 
noble in town, Baron Pine.</font>

337
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

338
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:42,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

339
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nana is indeed the daughter 
of Baron Tigui Pine.</font>

340
00:21:47,970 --> 00:21:49,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the nobles find out, 
it could be troublesome.</font>

341
00:21:50,990 --> 00:21:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. van Bate, bring Nana 
here tomorrow morning.</font>

342
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come at the usual lesson time.</font>

343
00:21:55,840 --> 00:21:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't draw attention.</font>

344
00:21:56,830 --> 00:21:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

345
00:21:58,620 --> 00:22:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barov, once Nana arrives tomorrow,</font>

346
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">take her directly to the kitchen.</font>

347
00:22:02,910 --> 00:22:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Clear the area beforehand.</font>

348
00:22:04,670 --> 00:22:06,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll meet her in the kitchen.</font>

349
00:22:06,690 --> 00:22:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very wise, Your Highness.</font>

350
00:22:39,830 --> 00:22:41,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

351
00:22:41,580 --> 00:22:42,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Pine is here.</font>

352
00:22:53,250 --> 00:22:54,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right.</font>

353
00:22:55,860 --> 00:22:57,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on, Nana.</font>

354
00:22:58,320 --> 00:22:59,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Greet His Highness.</font>

355
00:23:01,850 --> 00:23:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hello.</font>

356
00:23:03,380 --> 00:23:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm Nana Pine, Your Highness.</font>

357
00:23:07,950 --> 00:23:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, Miss Pine.</font>

358
00:23:11,040 --> 00:23:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome. Please have a seat.</font>

359
00:23:20,710 --> 00:23:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on, it's fine.</font>

360
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness is asking you to sit.</font>

361
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go ahead, it's all right.</font>

362
00:23:26,540 --> 00:23:27,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on.</font>

363
00:23:27,140 --> 00:23:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Pine,</font>

364
00:23:28,840 --> 00:23:30,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">may I also call you Nana?</font>

365
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:33,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here is some food.</font>

366
00:23:33,020 --> 00:23:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope you like it.</font>

367
00:24:07,280 --> 00:24:08,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nana.</font>

368
00:24:11,660 --> 00:24:13,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister Anna!</font>

369
00:24:17,210 --> 00:24:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness! Sister Anna, you're alive!</font>

370
00:24:20,450 --> 00:24:22,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They all said you were dead,</font>

371
00:24:22,160 --> 00:24:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I knew they were lying.</font>

372
00:24:26,950 --> 00:24:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've missed you so much.</font>

373
00:24:31,770 --> 00:24:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, time is short.</font>

374
00:24:33,570 --> 00:24:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must return to the 
construction site immediately.</font>

375
00:24:35,490 --> 00:24:37,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will never fail to 
meet your expectations.</font>

376
00:24:38,380 --> 00:24:41,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anna and Nana... 
I entrust them to your care.</font>

377
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:45,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So delicious, Sister Anna!</font>

378
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nana.</font>

379
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:49,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard from Professor Karl</font>

380
00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that you've also awakened as a witch.</font>

381
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When did it start?</font>

382
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:57,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you discover it?</font>

383
00:24:58,340 --> 00:24:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you tell me about it?</font>

384
00:25:02,840 --> 00:25:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About a week ago,</font>

385
00:25:05,420 --> 00:25:07,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw a little bird with a broken leg,</font>

386
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I really wanted to help it.</font>

387
00:25:09,380 --> 00:25:14,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, I felt something 
flow out from my palm,</font>

388
00:25:14,300 --> 00:25:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">like a ball of sticky water,</font>

389
00:25:16,420 --> 00:25:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it enveloped the bird.</font>

390
00:25:18,100 --> 00:25:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

391
00:25:19,790 --> 00:25:20,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then?</font>

392
00:25:21,280 --> 00:25:22,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then...</font>

393
00:25:22,890 --> 00:25:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then the bird was healed!</font>

394
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carter.</font>

395
00:25:27,090 --> 00:25:28,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Yes, Your Highness?</font>

396
00:25:29,360 --> 00:25:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go into town immediately.</font>

397
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:32,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find a hunter and buy some small animals—</font>

398
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:35,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">injured ones, dying ones, and dead ones.</font>

399
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get a few of each.</font>

400
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:38,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

401
00:25:50,890 --> 00:25:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nana, could you show me 
that sticky ball of water again?</font>

402
00:25:57,080 --> 00:25:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you want to help them?</font>

403
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:01,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

404
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:30,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're so cute.</font>

405
00:26:32,710 --> 00:26:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look.</font>

406
00:26:34,790 --> 00:26:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damaged parts can be healed.</font>

407
00:26:37,390 --> 00:26:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Severed limbs can be perfectly reattached.</font>

408
00:26:40,460 --> 00:26:42,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if the limb is lost,</font>

409
00:26:42,360 --> 00:26:44,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it cannot be regenerated.</font>

410
00:26:45,220 --> 00:26:46,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And...</font>

411
00:26:47,420 --> 00:26:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">death cannot be reversed.</font>

412
00:26:54,430 --> 00:26:57,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This power is incredible.</font>

413
00:26:58,210 --> 00:27:00,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saving lives and healing the 
wounded is a knight's duty.</font>

414
00:27:01,280 --> 00:27:02,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet, it is this little girl</font>

415
00:27:03,460 --> 00:27:06,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who has shown me what 
healing truly looks like.</font>

416
00:27:06,940 --> 00:27:10,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really... don't know what to say.</font>

417
00:27:11,970 --> 00:27:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, I'm beginning to 
understand your approach to witches.</font>

418
00:27:15,190 --> 00:27:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carter.</font>

419
00:27:16,010 --> 00:27:17,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Highness.</font>

420
00:27:17,520 --> 00:27:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take her home later.</font>

421
00:27:19,360 --> 00:27:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From now on, find opportunities 
to bring her here every day,</font>

422
00:27:21,880 --> 00:27:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so she can practice her powers.</font>

423
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not just keep her here?</font>

424
00:27:26,330 --> 00:27:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her powers are truly astonishing.</font>

425
00:27:29,610 --> 00:27:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her family is nobility.</font>

426
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:34,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nana hasn't been exposed as a witch yet.</font>

427
00:27:34,100 --> 00:27:35,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we brought her here now,</font>

428
00:27:35,970 --> 00:27:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it might prematurely start a 
conflict with the local nobles.</font>

429
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:42,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we're not ready for that yet.</font>

430
00:27:42,910 --> 00:27:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, do you truly believe that</font>

431
00:27:45,520 --> 00:27:49,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we can survive the Months of Demons here,</font>

432
00:27:49,010 --> 00:27:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with just that wall and 
the power of witches?</font>

433
00:27:51,270 --> 00:27:52,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

434
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:56,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this alone won't be enough.</font>

435
00:27:57,790 --> 00:27:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because besides the demonic beasts,</font>

436
00:28:00,320 --> 00:28:02,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we have many more enemies.</font>

437
00:28:05,970 --> 00:28:09,640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Translator: Henry Lin
Timer: Henry Lin
Editor: Zachary Carlysle
 QC: William Haggard</font>

